snippet.title: The First Descendent - Season One Gameplay Overview Trailer | gamescom 2024
snippet.description: Season one details for The First Descendent have been revealed, showcasing New invasion dungeons, powers, ultimates, and a new scout, Hailey Scott coming August 29th.
